<title>USA: Haas Neuveux says buys Polo Management.</title>
<headline>Haas Neuveux says buys Polo Management.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Haas Neuveux and Co has acquired 100 percent of the Polo Management Group, which includes the United Kingdom Polo Management Co., Wild Oats Ltd., the Punta del Esta Polo Club development project in Uruguay and Punta Polo Inc for an undisclosed price.</p>
<p>Current combined operating revenues are projected to exceed $1 million annually, with projections for fiscal year 1998 in excess of $2 million.</p>
